docs.abstract: New York Gov Andrew M Cuomo easily wins re-election, defeating conservative Westchester County Executive Rob Astorino; Cuomo's victory comes despite mixed feelings on part of voters and he enters his second term with less political clout than when campaign began, and with an uncertain future.
